For this choice of ${\tilde \theta}$ we have:
\begin{eqnarray}
 \frac{\langle S^z_{\bf 0}\rangle}{\sqrt{N}}  &=& \cos{\theta} - \frac{15}{64} \cos{\tilde \theta} x^4 + {\cal O}(\Delta^5_2)
\nonumber \\
\frac{|\langle S^z_{{\bf Q}_3}\rangle|^2}{N}  &=& \cos^2{\! \tilde \theta} \left [ \frac{ x^2}{2}
+ \frac{3x^4}{8} \right]  +{\cal O}(\Delta^6_2) 
\nonumber \\
\frac{|\langle S^z_{2{\bf Q}_3}\rangle|^2}{N}  &=&  \cos^2{\! \tilde \theta} \frac{x^4}{32} + {\cal O}(\Delta^6_2)
